receiving an mba from the university of chicago and after graduating from the wharton school at the university of pennsylvania  mr comizio will become a partner and the senior portfolio manager for medley credit strategies llc   this transaction combines the analytical and credit strengths of the two organizations  as a capital solutions provider to the middle market the addition of rob and his team will further enhance our debt and credit focused investment process and provides broader market perspectives and opportunities to both the borrower community and to our investors said brook taube managing partner at medley having known the medley team for some time i am excited about the opportunity to leverage our combined resources and to grow the firms investment management and advisory franchise added robert comizio about medley capital medley is a registered investment adviser with  billion of assets under management in private investment funds hedge funds and medley capital corporation nyse mcc a business development company  the firm specializes in credit investing including direct private lending and corporate credit related strategies  medley with  employees is headquartered in new york with offices in san francisco  medley investors include public and private pension funds endowment funds insurance companies institutional investors and alternative investment managers  for more information about the firm please visit wwwmedleycapitalcom source medley capital llc related links httpwwwmedleycapitalcom view table fullscreen view table fullscreen journalists and bloggers the news you need when you need it join pr newswire for journalists to access all of the free services designated to make your job easier in need of subject matter experts for your story submit a free profnet request and find the sources you need learn more my news release contains wide tables view fullscreen looking to send a news release with pr newswire take advantage of the worlds leading distri