ent process and provides broader market perspectives and opportunities to both the borrower community and to our investors like this article  get the free daily newsletter print email furtherreading from hedgeweek best wishes for  from the global fund media team fri    best wishes for  from the global fund media team wed    hedgeweek usa awards  – last chance to vote thu    hedgeweek global awards  – voting now closed thu    gottex reports positive performance for alternative and multiasset product lines tue    from our other sites low rates and new regulations keep market conditions challenging says greenwich associates wed    beringea’s portfolio company abzena raises gbpm through aim listing wed    changes to barclays ofi steelpath midstream mlp index tue    ccp closes usdm healthcare pe fund tue    powershares canada adds two etfs to smart beta line tue    features guides  guide to setting up an alternative investment fund in europe wed   blogs building investment fund structures  from startup to stardom tue   before you head to the beach… fri   the cftc provides more robust protection to whistleblowers wed   awards hedgeweek global awards  thu   special reports cybersecurity in europe  wed   mitigating compliance risk for pe managers thu   sei blockchain  building ecosystems in financial services fri   mifid ii meeting the compliance challenge sat   investment opportunities in infrastructure debt thu   events total alts thursday september     catalyst cap intro ls equity  event driven investing monday september     intralinks insights briefing  lp survey thursday september     altso’s th annual rocktoberfest thursday october     mining investment middle east and central asia  monday october     all events training international trade finance – dubai sun   international securities settlements  custodial services  dubai tue   emir fri   international payments mon   strategic corporate governance  kuwait tue   all courses listingsdirectory augentius thu   ikonic f